[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":559},["ShallowReactive",2],{"post-/topics/life":3},[4,89],{"_path":5,"_dir":6,"_draft":7,"_partial":7,"_locale":6,"title":8,"description":9,"type":10,"author":11,"date":14,"last_modified_date":14,"slug":15,"dropdown":16,"meta":17,"canonicalUrl":28,"topics":29,"body":32,"_type":84,"_id":85,"_source":86,"_file":87,"_stem":15,"_extension":88},"/continuous-learning-by-continuous-confusion-in-tech","",false,"Continuous learning by continuous confusion in tech","A key to becoming a good developer is continuously learning.","post",{"name":12,"image":13},"Cody Bontecou","https://codybontecou.com/images/cody-abstract.jpeg","2023-03-22T00:00:00.000Z","continuous-learning-by-continuous-confusion-in-tech","Misc",[18,20,22,24,26],{"name":19,"content":9},"og:description",{"name":21,"content":9},"og:image:alt",{"name":23,"content":8},"og:title",{"name":25,"content":8},"twitter:title",{"name":27,"content":8},"twitter:text:title","https://codybontecou.com/continuous-learning-by-continuous-confusion-in-tech.html",[30,31],"Life","Learning",{"type":33,"children":34,"toc":81},"root",[35,45,55,71,76],{"type":36,"tag":37,"props":38,"children":39},"element","h1",{"id":6},[40],{"type":36,"tag":41,"props":42,"children":44},"binding",{"value":43},"$frontmatter.title",[],{"type":36,"tag":46,"props":47,"children":48},"blockquote",{},[49],{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":51,"children":52},"p",{},[53],{"type":54,"value":9},"text",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":56,"children":57},{},[58,60,69],{"type":54,"value":59},"I'm taking the ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":62,"children":66},"a",{"href":63,"rel":64},"https://ionicframework.com/",[65],"nofollow",[67],{"type":54,"value":68},"Ionic Framework's",{"type":54,"value":70}," Vue tutorial, exposing me to things I need help understanding. But each step in the tutorial gives me a better understanding of the last.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":72,"children":73},{},[74],{"type":54,"value":75},"While I may need help understanding the content initially, it gives me a repository of codebases I can look back on whenever I need to solve a particular problem. Today, it's the Camera, Filesystem, and Storage APIs. If I ever face these problems in the future, I know where to look.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":77,"children":78},{},[79],{"type":54,"value":80},"Continuously following and exploring these frameworks and their documentation to build personal apps is why I am a \"Senior Fullstack Engineer.\" Nothing has prepared me better for work than getting lost in tutorials.",{"title":6,"searchDepth":82,"depth":82,"links":83},2,[],"markdown","content:continuous-learning-by-continuous-confusion-in-tech.md","content","continuous-learning-by-continuous-confusion-in-tech.md","md",{"_path":90,"_dir":6,"_draft":7,"_partial":7,"_locale":6,"title":91,"description":92,"type":10,"author":93,"date":95,"dropdown":16,"meta":96,"canonicalUrl":105,"topics":106,"body":107,"_type":84,"_id":556,"_source":86,"_file":557,"_stem":558,"_extension":88},"/dopamine-fasting-with-100-days-of-code","Dopamine Fasting with 100DaysOfCode","I'm going to spend the next 100 days taking a dopamine fast while spending the saved time writing code and sharing it with the community.",{"name":12,"image":94},"https://codybontecou.comhttps://codybontecou.com/images/cody-abstract.jpeg","2020-07-16T00:00:00.000Z",[97,98,101,103,104],{"name":23,"content":91},{"name":99,"content":100},"og:image","https://codybontecou.com/images/dopamine-fasting-meta.png",{"name":21,"content":102},"Man sitting at computer overloaded by media. 100 Days of Code While Dopamine Fasting.",{"name":25,"content":91},{"name":27,"content":91},"https://codybontecou.com/dopamine-fasting-with-100-days-of-code",[30],{"type":33,"children":108,"toc":551},[109,115,123,136,141,155,162,169,273,281,287,495,500,506,514,519,524,529,534,539,544],{"type":36,"tag":37,"props":110,"children":112},{"id":111},"dopamine-fasting-with-100daysofcode",[113],{"type":54,"value":114},"Dopamine Fasting with #100DaysOfCode",{"type":36,"tag":46,"props":116,"children":117},{},[118],{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":119,"children":120},{},[121],{"type":54,"value":122},"I'm stuck in a loop of consuming different means of entertainment and I want to alter this behavior, spending this time pursuing fulfilling goals.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":124,"children":125},{},[126,128,134],{"type":54,"value":127},"The dopamine fast is there to place strict rules on certain ",{"type":36,"tag":129,"props":130,"children":131},"strong",{},[132],{"type":54,"value":133},"activities I believe are not making my life better",{"type":54,"value":135},". As I consume less artificial stimulation, I believe I will get bored and find other, healthier activities to spend my time on.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":137,"children":138},{},[139],{"type":54,"value":140},"Rather than video games and movies every day, I will be coding, spending time with loved ones, and going on adventures.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":142,"children":143},{},[144,146,153],{"type":54,"value":145},"The ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":147,"children":150},{"href":148,"rel":149},"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23100DaysOfCode",[65],[151],{"type":54,"value":152},"#100DaysOfCode",{"type":54,"value":154}," is there to motivate myself and stay on track, but the goal is that this will be a lifelong change and continue well past the 100 days. I enjoy coding quite a bit and have been coding nearly everyday for years now, but I am taking the initiative to share my code so that it may help others.",{"type":36,"tag":156,"props":157,"children":161},"img",{"src":158,"alt":159,"width":160,"height":160},"https://codybontecou.com/images/character-003.png","Illustrated character",300,[],{"type":36,"tag":163,"props":164,"children":166},"h2",{"id":165},"rules",[167],{"type":54,"value":168},"Rules",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":171,"children":172},"ul",{},[173,179,184,189,194,212,250],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":175,"children":176},"li",{},[177],{"type":54,"value":178},"Code minimum an hour every day for the next 100 days.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":180,"children":181},{},[182],{"type":54,"value":183},"Tweet your progress every day with the #100DaysOfCode hashtag.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":185,"children":186},{},[187],{"type":54,"value":188},"No video games",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":190,"children":191},{},[192],{"type":54,"value":193},"No watching live streams",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":195,"children":196},{},[197,199],{"type":54,"value":198},"No movies or shows\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":200,"children":201},{},[202,207],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":203,"children":204},{},[205],{"type":54,"value":206},"Occasional movie nights with my wife are allowed",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":208,"children":209},{},[210],{"type":54,"value":211},"I just want to avoid consistently watching movies and shows",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":213,"children":214},{},[215,217],{"type":54,"value":216},"No music\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":218,"children":219},{},[220,233],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":221,"children":222},{},[223,225],{"type":54,"value":224},"Occasional podcasts are allowed\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":226,"children":227},{},[228],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":229,"children":230},{},[231],{"type":54,"value":232},"I'm thinking a 1-2 hour per day limit",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":234,"children":235},{},[236,238],{"type":54,"value":237},"Occasional music is allowed\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":239,"children":240},{},[241,245],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":242,"children":243},{},[244],{"type":54,"value":232},{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":246,"children":247},{},[248],{"type":54,"value":249},"I just want to avoid consistently listening to music",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":251,"children":252},{},[253,255],{"type":54,"value":254},"I only can interact with endlessly scrolling apps using their APIs\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":256,"children":257},{},[258,263,268],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":259,"children":260},{},[261],{"type":54,"value":262},"No feed queries - Only post update, and reply",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":264,"children":265},{},[266],{"type":54,"value":267},"This is subject to change depending on the endpoints available. The key is to avoid endlessly scrolling so I will build out my interaction apps with that in mind.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":269,"children":270},{},[271],{"type":54,"value":272},"Tutorials are allowed",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":274,"children":275},{},[276],{"type":36,"tag":156,"props":277,"children":280},{"alt":278,"src":279},"Illustrated forest","https://codybontecou.com/images/forest-2.png",[],{"type":36,"tag":163,"props":282,"children":284},{"id":283},"goals",[285],{"type":54,"value":286},"Goals",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":288,"children":289},{},[290,308,357,452,482],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":291,"children":292},{},[293,300],{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":294,"children":297},{"href":295,"rel":296},"https://www.typescriptlang.org/",[65],[298],{"type":54,"value":299},"Typescript",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":301,"children":302},{},[303],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":304,"children":305},{},[306],{"type":54,"value":307},"I plan on seriously diving into Typescript over the next 100 days. I know I'm missing out on key features by writing raw Javascript, so this is goal #1. Every personal project moving forward will be in Typescript.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":309,"children":310},{},[311,313],{"type":54,"value":312},"Learning conversation-level Spanish",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":314,"children":315},{},[316],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":317,"children":318},{},[319,321],{"type":54,"value":320},"I just recently got married to my lovely wife Daniela who is from Mexico. While she speaks English at a fluent level, a lot of her family does not. Now that we're married, there's no excuse. I will be reading and studying Spanish daily during this challenge. My study plan:\n",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":322,"children":323},{},[324,338,352],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":325,"children":326},{},[327,329,336],{"type":54,"value":328},"Read ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":330,"children":333},{"href":331,"rel":332},"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P6YRC1X/ref=dp-kindle-redirect?_encoding=UTF8&btkr=1",[65],[334],{"type":54,"value":335},"Accelerated Spanish",{"type":54,"value":337}," - not an affiliate link",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":339,"children":340},{},[341,343,350],{"type":54,"value":342},"Build out an ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":344,"children":347},{"href":345,"rel":346},"https://ankiweb.net/",[65],[348],{"type":54,"value":349},"Anki",{"type":54,"value":351}," deck with the words I learn from the book and study it daily",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":353,"children":354},{},[355],{"type":54,"value":356},"Practice with my wife and her family",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":358,"children":359},{},[360,362],{"type":54,"value":361},"Backend Typescript",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":363,"children":364},{},[365,379,408],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":366,"children":367},{},[368,370,377],{"type":54,"value":369},"I've written most of my server-side programs and REST APIs in Python (",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":371,"children":374},{"href":372,"rel":373},"https://www.djangoproject.com/",[65],[375],{"type":54,"value":376},"Django",{"type":54,"value":378},"). I've recently begun writing some simple scripts using NodeJS and plan on moving forward with NodeJS to have full-stack apps purely in Typescript.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":380,"children":381},{},[382,384],{"type":54,"value":383},"This attracts me for several reasons:\n",{"type":36,"tag":385,"props":386,"children":387},"ol",{},[388,393,398,403],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":389,"children":390},{},[391],{"type":54,"value":392},"I'm a big fan of web-based applications where Javascript (and Typescript) reign as supreme overlord.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":394,"children":395},{},[396],{"type":54,"value":397},"I'm already very comfortable writing frontend Javascript, so I hope picking up backend isn't too complicated.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":399,"children":400},{},[401],{"type":54,"value":402},"I'd like to master a programming language.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":404,"children":405},{},[406],{"type":54,"value":407},"The community is welcoming and enjoyable to be around.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":409,"children":410},{},[411,418,420,426],{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":412,"children":415},{"href":413,"rel":414},"https://www.fastify.io/",[65],[416],{"type":54,"value":417},"fastify",{"type":54,"value":419}," - ",{"type":36,"tag":421,"props":422,"children":423},"em",{},[424],{"type":54,"value":425},"\"Fast and low overhead web framework, for Node.js\"",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":427,"children":428},{},[429],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":430,"children":431},{},[432,434,441,443,450],{"type":54,"value":433},"I plan on following ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":435,"children":438},{"href":436,"rel":437},"https://twitter.com/wolfejw86",[65],[439],{"type":54,"value":440},"Jay Wolfe's",{"type":54,"value":442}," comprehensive ",{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":444,"children":447},{"href":445,"rel":446},"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLU_22oKqONin7yagFMm3x1tJihYaIVVwa",[65],[448],{"type":54,"value":449},"Fastify tutorial",{"type":54,"value":451}," and see where it takes me.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":453,"children":454},{},[455,457],{"type":54,"value":456},"Testing",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":458,"children":459},{},[460,465,477],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":461,"children":462},{},[463],{"type":54,"value":464},"I'd like to become more confident in applying TDD within my applications.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":466,"children":467},{},[468,475],{"type":36,"tag":61,"props":469,"children":472},{"href":470,"rel":471},"https://www.cypress.io/blog/2021/04/06/introducing-the-cypress-component-test-runner/",[65],[473],{"type":54,"value":474},"Cypress Component Test Runner",{"type":54,"value":476}," is extremely exciting and I plan on becoming more comfortable with this for my web components.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":478,"children":479},{},[480],{"type":54,"value":481},"Testing different states within my components is still challenging to me. By the end of this challenge, I want to be able to replicate different states within my application.",{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":483,"children":484},{},[485,487],{"type":54,"value":486},"Component Driven Development",{"type":36,"tag":170,"props":488,"children":489},{},[490],{"type":36,"tag":174,"props":491,"children":492},{},[493],{"type":54,"value":494},"Alongside Cypress, I want to be building web components that are interactive, scalable, and flexible.",{"type":36,"tag":156,"props":496,"children":499},{"src":497,"alt":498,"width":160,"height":160},"https://codybontecou.com/images/luggage.png","Illustrated luggage bag with soon on it",[],{"type":36,"tag":163,"props":501,"children":503},{"id":502},"why",[504],{"type":54,"value":505},"Why?",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":507,"children":508},{},[509],{"type":36,"tag":129,"props":510,"children":511},{},[512],{"type":54,"value":513},"I'm finding it hard to focus.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":515,"children":516},{},[517],{"type":54,"value":518},"I may start my day with an hour or two of World of Warcraft (WoW), maybe a few Youtube videos, Reddit threads, finally get some work in around 11 am, take a break for lunch, and rinse and repeat with a \"quick\" session of WoW, YouTube, etc...",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":520,"children":521},{},[522],{"type":54,"value":523},"This has been going on for months now, and I believe it's time to try something drastic to alter my behavior.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":525,"children":526},{},[527],{"type":54,"value":528},"I've tried scheduling my days - work in the morning, a game in the afternoon - but I always feel bad about my decisions by the time I go to bed. I have goals in life and I want to be spending my time outside of work striving to achieve those goals.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":530,"children":531},{},[532],{"type":54,"value":533},"Of course, life isn't all about work and achieving goals, but I also want to spend my free time doing things like being with my wife, going on camping trips, and helping my community.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":535,"children":536},{},[537],{"type":54,"value":538},"I think cutting the time-consuming, unfulfilling behaviors out of my life will open up the time and energy to live an exciting, fulfilling life.",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":540,"children":541},{},[542],{"type":54,"value":543},"Join me in this journey,",{"type":36,"tag":50,"props":545,"children":546},{},[547],{"type":36,"tag":129,"props":548,"children":549},{},[550],{"type":54,"value":12},{"title":6,"searchDepth":82,"depth":82,"links":552},[553,554,555],{"id":165,"depth":82,"text":168},{"id":283,"depth":82,"text":286},{"id":502,"depth":82,"text":505},"content:dopamine-fasting-with-100-days-of-code.md","dopamine-fasting-with-100-days-of-code.md","dopamine-fasting-with-100-days-of-code",1731091702279]